狀。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　110 　年　　8 　　月　　17　　日\r\n                              書記官  鍾佩芳","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SCDM/110%2c%e5%96%ae%e7%a6%81%e6%b2%92%2c82%2c20210817%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SCDM,110,單禁沒,82,20210817,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"單禁沒","JNO":"82","JDATE":"20210817","JTITLE":"聲請單獨宣告沒收違禁物"}